data.description: Perfect haven for animal enthusiasts! Gorgeous home on 9+ acres just outside of beautiful Bowling Green! This home has been upgraded and refreshed from the roof to the basement. Granite countertops, gas range, Fridge less than a year old. Very bright Chef's kitchen flows to the eat in space and into the family room. Bright, sunny and oh so cozy! Gas built in range and double wall ovens This home has formal dining room and living room that makes entertaining a breeze. Upstairs features 3 bedrooms, and a large primary suite complete with walk in closet. Bonus laundry room makes doing laundry easy. New carpet as well as a complete refresh that enhances the bright sunlight and airy feeling. The basement has a woodstove and is already plumbed for a full bath. The outside living space makes for some great entertaining or just relaxing beside the 18 foot firepit. Sellers had 2 horses that enjoyed great pasture space and barn. double sheds on property that have great storage space for outside tools. Brand new HVAC units on both floors, paved driveway. We can't wait for you to see the property!
